data.description: Welcome Home! Don't allow this great opportunity to slip by. Less than 10 mins from World Golf Village. This home is in the desired community of Trailmark. This home is still fairly new with minor cosmetic repairs. Updated kitchen. Lots of space to host events for the holidays. Family oriented neighborhood. Tons of amenities. This is definitely a bargain. The sellers are very motivated and ready to move on. This home is only 3 yrs old and ready for its new owner. This home is being sold AS IS. The sellers will not make any repairs.
